data.description: Just picture the pool parties you could host this summer! This Maplewood residence boasts mature trees in the front yard, a welcoming front porch perfect for rocking chairs, and a charming neighborhood ideal for leisurely walks or bike rides. Inside, discover gleaming hardwood floors, stainless steel appliances, two pantries, and main level laundry. Upstairs, the bedrooms feature NEW CARPETING, with an ensuite primary bedroom at the end of the hallway. If you love the outdoors, step out onto the deck and create your own retreat in the backyard with an above-ground pool and wooden fence. Conveniently located just 10 minutes from both TTU and CRMC, this property offers an excellent location. New Trane HVAC installed upstairs-2021
